5. Keep bullets sharp and business-ready:
   - Max 6 bullets
   - Max 25 words per bullet
   - No nested JSON
   - Clear FP&A storytelling style (like management commentary)

6. Summaries must be output in STRICT JSON format as below:

{
  "level": "<level>",
  "executive_summary": [
      "bullet 1",
