      "explain drivers at L4/L5/L6 level",
      "highlight any product or cost center causing variance"
  ],
  "risks_and_opportunities": [
      "risk bullet",
      "opportunity bullet"
  ]
}

Do NOT add explanations.
Do NOT create nested JSON.
Return ONLY valid JSON.
